show.description: Betrayed by his wife, abandoned by life… but fate turned him into a miraculous doctor! This is the extraordinary redemption story of a security guard who became a supernatural healer. Now, he holds divine knowledge of medicine, costing, and healing. Listen to The Sage Doctor, where every wound has a cure!
